  <brief_title>Prospective Construction and Validation of a Prognostic Score to Identify Among Patients With Metastatic Breast Cancer Those Who Benefit From a Third Line Chemotherapy in Terms of Overall Survival</brief_title>
  <acronym>METAL3</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective Construction and Validation of a Prognostic Score to Identify Among Patients With Metastatic Breast Cancer Those Who Benefit From a Third Line Chemotherapy in Terms of Overall Survival</official_title>
